---
title: Peachy Pork Tacos with Tangy Summer Slaw
description: Pork pairs with almost any fruit—apples, figs, pineapple, you name it! We particularly love the combination of pork chops and peach salsa inside these summery tacos. A crunchy vinegar-based slaw adds the perfect bite to each taco.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/peachy-pork-tacos-b1d5d1c0.jpg
